443\u043b\u044c\u0442\u0430\u0446\u0438\u044f<\/h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; outline: 0px;\">\u041d\u0430\u0448\u0438 \u0441\u043f\u0435\u0446\u0438\u0430\u043b\u0438\u0441\u0442\u044b \u0433\u043e\u0442\u043e\u0432\u044b 24\/7 \u043a\u043e\u043d\u0441\u0443\u043b\u044c\u0442\u0438\u0440\u043e\u0432\u0430\u0442\u044c \u043f\u043e \u043b\u044e\u0431\u044b\u043c \u0432\u043e\u043f\u0440\u043e\u0441\u0430\u043c, \u0441\u0432\u044f\u0437\u0430\u043d\u043d\u044b\u043c \u0441 \u0436\u0435\u043b\u0430\u043d\u0438\u0435\u043c \u043a\u0443\u043f\u0438\u0442\u044c \u0430\u0432\u0442\u043e \u0438\u0437 \u0421\u0428\u0410 \u0431\/\u0443. \u0417\u0430 \u043a\u043e\u043d\u0441\u0443\u043b\u044c\u0442\u0430\u0446\u0438\u0438 \u043d\u0435 \u043d\u0443\u0436\u043d\u043e \u043f\u043b\u0430\u0442\u0438\u0442\u044c \u0434\u043e\u043f\u043e\u043b\u043d\u0438\u0442\u0435\u043b\u044c\u043d\u043e, \u043d\u0430\u0448\u0430 \u0432\u043d\u0443\u0442\u0440\u0435\u043d\u043d\u044f\u044f \u043f\u043e\u043b\u0438\u0442\u0438\u043a\u0430 \u043f\u0440\u0435\u0434\u0443\u0441\u043c\u0430\u0442\u0440\u0438\u0432\u0430\u0435\u0442 \u0440\u0430\u0431\u043e\u0442\u0443 \u0441 \u043a\u043b\u0438\u0435\u043d\u0442\u043e\u043c \u043a\u0430\u043a \u0434\u043e \u0437\u0430\u043a\u043b\u044e\u0447\u0435\u043d\u0438\u044f \u0434\u043e\u0433\u043e\u0432\u043e\u0440\u0430, \u0442\u0430\u043a \u0438 \u043f\u043e\u0441\u043b\u0435 \u0442\u0440\u0430\u043d\u0441\u043f\u043e\u0440\u0442\u0438\u0440\u043e\u0432\u043a\u0438 \u0430\u0432\u0442\u043e\u043c\u043e\u0431\u0438\u043b\u044f \u0432 \u0423\u043a\u0440\u0430\u0438\u043d\u0443.<\/p><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 0px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 43px; font-size: 36px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-caps: small-caps; outline: 0px;\">\u0420\u0435\u043c\u043e\u043d\u0442 \u0430\u043c\u0435\u0440\u0438\u043a\u0430\u043d\u0441\u043a\u0438\u0445 \u0430\u0432\u0442\u043e \u0438 \u043f\u043e\u0434\u0431\u043e\u0440 \u0437\u0430\u043f\u0447\u0430\u0441\u0442\u0435\u0439<\/h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; outline: 0px;\">\u0421\u043f\u0435\u0446\u0438\u0430\u043b\u044c\u043d\u043e \u0434\u043b\u044f \u043f\u043e\u043c\u043e\u0449\u0438 \u043a\u043b\u0438\u0435\u043d\u0442\u0430\u043c \u043e\u0442\u043a\u0440\u044b\u043b\u0438 \u0441\u043e\u0431\u0441\u0442\u0432\u0435\u043d\u043d\u0443\u044e \u0421\u0422\u041e, \u0433\u0434\u0435 \u043d\u0430\u0448\u0438 \u043c\u0435\u0445\u0430\u043d\u0438\u043a\u0438 \u043f\u0440\u043e\u0434\u0438\u0430\u0433\u043d\u043e\u0441\u0442\u0438\u0440\u0443\u044e\u0442 \u0430\u0432\u0442\u043e\u043c\u043e\u0431\u0438\u043b\u0438 \u0438\u0437 \u0421\u0428\u0410, \u043e\u0442\u0440\u0435\u043c\u043e\u043d\u0442\u0438\u0440\u0443\u044e\u0442 \u0438\u043b\u0438 \u043f\u043e\u043c\u043e\u0433\u0443\u0442 \u0437\u0430\u043a\u0430\u0437\u0430\u0442\u044c \u043d\u0435\u043e\u0431\u0445\u043e\u0434\u0438\u043c\u044b\u0435 \u0437\u0430\u043f\u0447\u0430\u0441\u0442\u0438, \u043a\u043e\u0442\u043e\u0440\u044b\u0435 \u043d\u0435 \u043d\u0430\u0439\u0434\u0435\u0448\u044c \u043d\u0430 \u0440\u044b\u043d\u043a\u0435 \u0423\u043a\u0440\u0430\u0438\u043d\u044b.<\/p><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 0px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 43px; font-size: 36px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-caps: small-caps; outline: 0px;\">\u0410\u0432\u0442\u043e\u043c\u043e\u0431\u0438\u043b\u044c \u0438\u0437 \u0410\u043c\u0435\u0440\u0438\u043a\u0438 \u043f\u043e\u0434 \u043a\u043b\u044e\u0447<\/h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; outline: 0px;\">\u041f\u0440\u0435\u0434\u043e\u0441\u0442\u0430\u0432\u043b\u044f\u0435\u043c \u0443\u0441\u043b\u0443\u0433\u0438 \u043f\u043e \u043f\u043e\u043a\u0443\u043f\u043a\u0435 \u0430\u0432\u0442\u043e \u0438\u0437 \u0421\u0428\u0410 \u043f\u043e\u0434 \u043a\u043b\u044e\u0447, \u043a\u043e\u0433\u0434\u0430 \u043a\u043b\u0438\u0435\u043d\u0442 \u0442\u043e\u043b\u044c\u043a\u043e \u043d\u0430\u0437\u044b\u0432\u0430\u0435\u0442 \u0441\u0432\u043e\u0439 \u0431\u044e\u0434\u0436\u0435\u0442, \u0430 \u043d\u0430\u0448\u0438 \u0441\u043f\u0435\u0446\u0438\u0430\u043b\u0438\u0441\u0442\u044b \u0441\u0430\u043c\u0438 \u0437\u0430\u043d\u0438\u043c\u0430\u044e\u0442\u0441\u044f \u043f\u043e\u0438\u0441\u043a\u043e\u043c \u0430\u0432\u0442\u043e, \u043f\u043e\u043a\u0443\u043f\u043a\u043e\u0439, \u0442\u0440\u0430\u043d\u0441\u043f\u043e\u0440\u0442\u0438\u0440\u043e\u0432\u043a\u043e\u0439 \u0432 \u0423\u043a\u0440\u0430\u0438\u043d\u0443, \u0442\u0430\u043c\u043e\u0436\u0435\u043d\u043d\u043e\u0439 \u043e\u0447\u0438\u0441\u0442\u043a\u043e\u0439 \u0438 \u043f\u043e\u0441\u0442\u0430\u043d\u043e\u0432\u043a\u043e\u0439 \u043d\u0430 \u0443\u0447\u0435\u0442.<\/p><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 0px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 43px; font-size: 36px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-caps: small-caps; outline: 0px;\">\u041a\u0443\u043f\u0438\u0442\u044c \u0430\u0432\u0442\u043e \u0437 \u0421\u0428\u0410<\/h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; outline: 0px;\">\u041a\u043e\u043c\u043f\u0430\u043d\u0438\u044f Bexhill Trading Auto \u0441 \u0440\u0430\u0434\u043e\u0441\u0442\u044c\u044e \u043f\u043e\u043c\u043e\u0436\u0435\u0442 \u0432\u044b\u0431\u0440\u0430\u0442\u044c, \u043f\u0440\u0438\u043e\u0431\u0440\u0435\u0441\u0442\u0438 \u0438 \u043f\u043e\u043b\u0443\u0447\u0438\u0442\u044c \u0430\u0432\u0442\u043e\u043c\u043e\u0431\u0438\u043b\u044c \u043c\u0435\u0447\u0442\u044b \u0438\u0437 \u0421\u0428\u0410. \u041c\u0435\u043d\u0435\u0434\u0436\u0435\u0440\u044b \u0443\u0447\u0442\u0443\u0442 \u0432\u0441\u0435 \u0442\u0440\u0435\u0431\u043e\u0432\u0430\u043d\u0438\u044f \u0438 \u043f\u043e\u0436\u0435\u043b\u0430\u043d\u0438\u044f, \u043e\u0431\u0440\u0430\u0442\u044f\u0442 \u0432\u043d\u0438\u043c\u0430\u043d\u0438\u0435 \u043d\u0430 \u043d\u044e\u0430\u043d\u0441\u044b \u043f\u043e\u043a\u0443\u043f\u043a\u0438 \u043a\u043e\u043d\u043a\u0440\u0435\u0442\u043d\u043e\u0439 \u043c\u043e\u0434\u0435\u043b\u0438 \u0438 \u0431\u0443\u0434\u0443\u0442 \u043d\u0430 \u0441\u0432\u044f\u0437\u0438 24 \u0447\u0430\u0441\u0430 \u0432 \u0441\u0443\u0442\u043a\u0438, \u0447\u0442\u043e\u0431\u044b \u043f\u0440\u043e\u043a\u043e\u043d\u0441\u0443\u043b\u044c\u0442\u0438\u0440\u043e\u0432\u0430\u0442\u044c \u043f\u043e \u0432\u043e\u043f\u0440\u043e\u0441\u0430\u043c, \u0441\u0432\u044f\u0437\u0430\u043d\u043d\u044b\u043c \u0441 \u0440\u0430\u0431\u043e\u0442\u043e\u0439 \u043a\u043e\u043c\u043f\u0430\u043d\u0438\u0438.<\/p>","en":"<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; outline: 0px;\">Bexhill Trading Auto is an official dealer of IAAI, Copart, Manheim in Ukraine, dealing with serfdom and selling cars from the USA. we are an official partner of car auctions such as IAAI, Copart and Manheim. At the same time, our company is actively developing in the east - we have been transporting cars from Korea for more than two years.<\/p><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 0px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 43px; font-size: 36px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-caps: small-caps; outline: 0px;\">Why import a car from the USA<\/h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px;\"><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"Montserrat, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">We compared the US markets with European ones and realized that buying a car in America is several times more profitable, no matter how paradoxical it may sound. This is due to thoughtful logistics, the level of development of services for assessing the condition of a car and the process of buying a car itself.<\/span><\/font><\/p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px;\"><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"Montserrat, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Most US citizens take a car on lease for several years and the leasing company itself is engaged in constant maintenance of the car during the entire period of operation, as a result of which cars from the USA are one of the best choices for car enthusiasts in Ukraine.<\/span><\/font><\/p><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 0px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 43px; font-size: 36px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-caps: small-caps; outline: 0px;\">Why such a low price?<\/h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; outline: 0px;\">Damaged cars from the USA are redeemed from auctions of insurance companies. At these auctions, the car loses half the price even due to minimal damage. If we take into account the cash costs, namely the ransom, delivery, customs and repairs, the price of a car similar in condition in Ukraine will be 35-50% higher, and new ones will cost space money.<\/p><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 0px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 43px; font-size: 36px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-caps: small-caps; outline: 0px;\">Complete sets of European and American cars<\/h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; outline: 0px;\">A distinctive feature of cars from the USA is the predominance of the complete set over the basic one. Therefore, a car in the \u201cmaximum speed\u201d will cost a little more than an \u201cempty\u201d car, so the most profitable solution is to buy a car from the USA in \u201cfull stuffing\u201d. You can read more in our article - \"The main differences between American cars and European ones.\"<\/p><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 0px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 43px; font-size: 36px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-caps: small-caps; outline: 0px;\">Mileage<\/h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; outline: 0px;\">We specifically select cars from America at low mileage auctions. This allows you to clearly understand in the future how the car will behave over a distance of several years.<\/p><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 0px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 43px; font-size: 36px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-caps: small-caps; outline: 0px;\">Service<\/h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; outline: 0px;\">The automotive service industry in America has evolved along with the global automotive industry. All Americans honestly undergo MOT, and records of this remain in the database, the car will be predictable with almost one hundred percent probability. The sale most often takes place without intermediaries.<\/p><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 0px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 43px; font-size: 36px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-caps: small-caps; outline: 0px;\">The lineup<\/h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; outline: 0px;\">Americans annually sell hundreds of thousands of personal cars of various brands at car auctions in the United States.<\/p><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 0px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 43px; font-size: 36px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-caps: small-caps; outline: 0px;\">The work of auctions with American cars:<\/h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px;\"><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"Montserrat, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">After gaining access to the auction, our employee makes a bet on the purchase of the car.<\/span><\/font><\/p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px;\"><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"Montserrat, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">The car goes to the one whose bid will be higher than the others. If the rate is successful, then the complex process of obtaining documents for the car begins, transportation to the company\'s site in the United States, then to the port and further to Ukraine.<\/span><\/font><\/p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px;\"><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"Montserrat, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">What does the client need? You need to declare the maximum cost of buying a car (this point is discussed even before bidding at the auction, based on the predicted price at the auction, a turnkey car in Ukraine is calculated).<\/span><\/font><\/p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px;\"><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"Montserrat, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Then the car sets sail for Ukraine. The transportation time is no more than 10 weeks from the moment of winning and registration of the car.<\/span><\/font><\/p><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 0px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 43px; font-size: 36px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-caps: small-caps; outline: 0px;\">Features of auctions<\/h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px;\"><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"Montserrat, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">As mentioned above, to participate in the auction, a person must have special access, so buying a car at an auction in the United States for an ordinary citizen of Ukraine will not be an easy task, but not for us. Bexhill Trading Auto received access to open and closed auctions, which allows you to buy a car from the USA, focusing on the client\'s advantages and carry out the delivery of a car in Ukraine on order.<\/span><\/font><\/p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px;\"><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"Montserrat, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Our customers order a car from the United States of America at a price 35-50% below the market price. Thousands of insurance company vehicles are sold at auctions every week, including diesel, gasoline, hybrids and electric vehicles. We can organize the transportation of the car not only to Ukraine, but also through the territory of Ukraine (except for the temporarily occupied territories of Donetsk and Luhansk regions, and the Autonomous Republic of Crimea).<\/span><\/font><\/p><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 0px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 43px; font-size: 36px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-caps: small-caps; outline: 0px;\">Why us?<\/h3><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 0px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 43px; font-size: 36px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-caps: small-caps; outline: 0px;\">Own car dealerships<\/h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; outline: 0px;\">Bexhill Trading Auto opened its own car dealerships in the cities of Ukraine: Kyiv, Odessa, Kharkov and Nikolaev. It is very important to us that customers feel safe in the process of buying and shipping a car from the USA. The number of salons subsequently only grows, it is planned to open branches in other cities of Ukraine, so that customers constantly choose cars from America.<\/p><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 0px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 43px; font-size: 36px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-caps: small-caps; outline: 0px;\">Intermediaries<\/h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; outline: 0px;\">Bexhill Trading Auto has entered into an agreement with intermediaries in the United States who help us bring the car safe and sound, compare the declared and real condition of the car, check the car and all units for hidden damage.<\/p><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 0px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 43px; font-size: 36px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-caps: small-caps; outline: 0px;\">Personal Area<\/h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; outline: 0px;\">Buyers after the conclusion of the transaction get access to the personal account of the Bexhill Trading Auto client, where they can monitor the status of the car, see the full amount of payments and other necessary information.<\/p><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 0px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 43px; font-size: 36px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-caps: small-caps; outline: 0px;\">Consultation<\/h3><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; outline: 0px;\">Our experts are ready 24\/7 to advise on any issues related to the desire to buy a used car from the USA. You do not need to pay extra for consultations, our internal policy provides for working with the client both before the conclusion of the contract and after the transportation of the car to Ukraine.<\/p><h3 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 0px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 43px; font-size: 36px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; 